                            <comment id="394417" author="sthiell" created="Mon, 27 Nov 2023 20:02:56 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Just to follow-up on this issue I reported: even after applying the workaround above, we had other LNet issues when using RoCE with Lustre on Broadcom NICs and realized that their RoCE support is actually not fully implemented with 57414 NICs. We switched to NVIDIA ConnectX-6 Lx NICs instead and RoCE seems to just work out of the box with Lustre.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
